1. *Rukama* je zatvorio vrata. (He closed the door with his hands.)
2. Ona je pamtila njegovu toplu *ruku* na njenoj ramenu. (She remembered his warm hand on her shoulder.)
3. On je pokupio stvari sa podova pomoÄ‡u svojih *rukama*. (He picked up the things from the floor using his hands.)
4. Ona je hodala rukama i nogama. (She walked on her hands and feet.)
5. Ona je pipala po mapi svojim *rukama*. (She felt the map with her hands.)
6. On je bio u stanju da radi nevjerovatne stvari samo svojim *rukama*. (He was able to do amazing things only with his hands.)